    Draft --> Parsed : User Input Text
    Parsed --> Categorized : NLP Processing
    
    Categorized --> Confirmed : User Confirmation
    Categorized --> Edited : User Edits
    Edited --> Confirmed : User Confirmation
    
    Confirmed --> Saved : API Success
    Saved --> [*]
    
    Saved --> Deleted : User Action
    Deleted --> [*]
